songs.title: Who Are You?
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
I want you by my side
The rain takes away my pain
But you take my bad time?
You tell me about you
But you did not tell me who are you
I know your voice
But I don't know if it's really you
I want to be afraid
I want to be afraid again
I know you
But I do not know who I know
I want to know who you are
I believe in your love
But I feel bad now
